    <div class="zr-head"><b>天星择日</b> · toạ <span class="zh">${t.sitting}</span> ${zi[t.sitting]} · hướng <span class="zh">${t.facing}</span> ${zi[t.facing]} · sơn ${t.mountainElementLabel} (${t.mountainSystem==="zhengti"?"正体":"化气"})</div>
